      <title>奥地利认为欧盟的预算谴责不可避免为螺旋螺旋</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/austria-sees-eu-budget-reprimand-unavoidable-as-deficit-spirals</link>
